Tammy Lynn Leppert https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tammy_Lynn_Leppert 0 Tammy Lynn Leppert (February 5, 1965 — disappeared July 6, 1983) is an American former child and teen model, actress and beauty queen who went missing under mysterious circumstances at the age of 18.
